OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly dry
OL,6,Fwith some bright spells at first but
OL,7,Fshowers become more frequent through
OL,8,Fthe evening and overnight. It will be
OL,9,Frather windy at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FIt will stay mainly dry in
OL,12,FEastern Borders with some bright
OL,13,Fspells at times. Cloudier in the west
OL,14,Fwith some showers, becoming drier
OL,15,Flater in the day. Windy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
