OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry and
OL,6,Fbecoming increasingly sunny on Sunday.
OL,7,FDry and bright start on Monday, rain
OL,8,Ffrom southwest later. Mostly cloudy
OL,9,FTuesday with rain or showers. Becoming
OL,10,Fwarmer.
